arStrings.szText: Lorath spoke of Lesser Evils beyond Andariel. Could that—thing—have been one?
panting, exhausted from a hard battle
The Horadrim should be at the palace...if they made it.
Lorath habló de otros demonios menores, aparte de Andariel. ¿Sería… eso… uno de ellos?
